div.p:
1516. I of course will comply with instructions contained in Deptel 820,
                            July 12; repeated telCan 446. In reaching decision that I visit Canton
                            en route Washington I assume you had in mind negative aspects of such
                            visit set forth in Canton’s telegram 612, June 19 to Department;
                            repeated Nanking 409, with which I agreed (see mytel 1317, June 18;
                            repeated Canton 547).
